CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 31, 1955, pg. A17 reads: "Holiday Fun - When the swank Frogs Club gave its annual holiday party at the Flamingo Tuesday night, this gay group was caught by the cameraman. Seated are Mrs. Henry Smith, Mrs. Florence Byrd Davis, Dr. Royal W. Taylor and Mrs. Homer S. Brown.  Standing are Jayne and Russell Shelton. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Henry Smith, Florence Byrd Davis, Dr. Royal W. Taylor, and Wilhelmina Byrd Brown seated behind banquet table, with Jayne Shelton, and Russell Shelton standing behind them, in Flamingo Club for FROGS holiday party
